e in the US a few decaded ago where a guy was thrown in jail for 10yrs for stealing a chocolate... he was still waiting for his actual trial But they forgot about him Cruel world cousin... @Himesh 100% agree... special treatment shows that the world just ain't fair... Generally yes... but some prisons are full of human rights violations Well if we did then we would also have to account for it Now we know what you would do Mbuso... Everyone is corruptible... that's true... but not everyone chooses to be corrupt...

